validatePutArguments(String[]) - Static method in class weloveclouds.client.commands.utils.ArgumentsValidator
A put command is valid, if:
(1) the ArgumentsValidator.KEY_INDEX parameter of arguments is a key, and
(2) all other parameters starting from ArgumentsValidator.VALUE_INDEX parameter of the arguments are regarded and merged as value, and
(3) these are the only arguments, and
(4) and the size of the key is at most ArgumentsValidator.KEY_SIZE_LIMIT_IN_BYTES bytes, and
(5) and the size of the value is at most ArgumentsValidator.VALUE_SIZE_LIMIT_IN_BYTES bytes.
